## ✅ Example 2: Cleaning up `setInterval`

```jsx
useEffect(() => {
  const timer = setInterval(() => {
    console.log("Running...");
  }, 1000);

  return () => {
    clearInterval(timer);
    console.log("Interval cleared on unmount");
  };
}, []);
```

